CallFire,provides,a,VoIP,platform,that,powers,voice,broadcasts,call,centers,call,tracking,and,text,messaging,campaigns,This,API,lets,users,create,recording,campaigns,Functionality,includes,retrieving,recordings,retrieving,sound,files,by,caller,ID,playback,recordings,and,more,The,API,uses,SOAP,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML